|rowspan="10"| [[Tokyu Corporation]]
{{JARC item|DT|168|Tokyu Den-en-Toshi Line|Den-en-Toshi Line}}
{{JARC item|IK|341|Tokyu Ikegami Line|Ikegami Line}}
{{JARC item|KD|206|Tokyu Kodomonokuni Line|Kodomonokuni Line}}
