! Operator !! Parameter !! Color !! {{left|Line}}
|}

=== Examples ===
{|class="wikitable"
! Code
! Result
|-
|<code><nowiki>{{color|{{Ja-rail-color|A}}|■}} Toei Asakusa Line</nowiki></code>
|{{color|{{Ja-rail-color|A}}|■}} Toei Asakusa Line
|-
|<code><nowiki>{{RouteBox|Narita Sky Access Line|Keisei Narita Airport Line|{{Ja-rail-color|KS|N}}|black}}</nowiki></code>
|{{RouteBox|Narita Sky Access Line|Keisei Narita Airport Line|{{Ja-rail-color|KS|N}}|black}}
|-
|<code><nowiki>{{JARC|Z}}</nowiki></code>
|{{JARC|Z}}
|-
|<code><nowiki>{{JARC|Z|#}}</nowiki></code>
|{{JARC|Z|#}}
|}

