{{Documentation subpage}}

{{template shortcut|JARC}}

This template returns a [[hex code]] for the colors of Japanese rail services and rapid transit lines.

In order to call a line's color, the code <code>&#123;&#123;Ja-rail-color|<i>service</i>}}</code> is used (where ''service'' is replaced by the appropriate abbreviation for the service or line.

Adding {{code|#}} as the optional second parameter will suppress the normally-included preceding # symbol (required for some templates).

*After saving an amendment, {{purge|purge this page}} to refresh the color samples.

